    • Method Detail

      • setScrollSpeed

        public void setScrollSpeed(float speed)
        Sets the scroll speed when dragging an item. Defaults to 1.0f.
        Parameters:
        speed - <1.0f to slow down scrolling, >1.0f to speed up scrolling.

      • startDragging

        public void startDragging(int position)
        Starts dragging the item at given position. User must be touching this DynamicListView.
        Parameters:
        position - the position of the item start dragging.
        Throws:
        IllegalStateException - if the user is not touching this DynamicListView.
